<h1>Gephex 0.4.1 Release Notes</h1>

<p>On October 29th 2004, the Gephex Project released Gephex 0.4.1</p>

<p>Gephex is a modular real-time video effect framework.
0.4.1 is a bugfix and stabilization release of the 0.4 branch.
It also introduces minor feature enhancements.
</p>

